<item>
            <title>[HBASE-10773] Make use of ByteRanges in HFileBlock instead of ByteBuffers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10773</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Replacing BBs with Byte Ranges  in block cache as part of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10772&quot; title=&quot;Use ByteRanges instead of ByteBuffers in BlockCache&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-10772&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-10772&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, would help in replacing BBs with BRs in HFileBlock also.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12701878">HBASE-10773</key>
            <summary>Make use of ByteRanges in HFileBlock instead of ByteBuffers</summary>
